name: Every End
author: MindCap
description: The hardest endurance level in Geometry Dash, featuring over 7 minutes of simple yet brutal 1.0 cube timings. Its difficulty balancing and specific skillset has lead it to being very accessible for a top level. Despite its simple 1.0 aesthetic, its technically impressive background effect involved the usage of third party software developed by Absolute. (Source: Aredl.net)
